imdb.plot outline: American foreign service brats Jeremiah J.J. Livingston, Paulina PEZHEAD Kingsley, Cal IRONMAN Miller, and Aimee JoJo Rauscher navigate third world garden spot deployments, diplomatic intrigues and love among war-torn antiquities as they unsuccessfully try to avoid dire consequences of nation building.
